46
00:03:54,840 --> 00:03:56,070
Yes, I bought them.

47
00:03:58,079 --> 00:03:59,440
Darling, I want the same.

48
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:00,500
Go away.

49
00:04:01,920 --> 00:04:03,470
