75
00:04:53,040 --> 00:04:54,030
Get out!

76
00:04:56,040 --> 00:04:57,110
Come on.

77
00:04:57,880 --> 00:04:59,240
It's here.

78
00:04:59,320 --> 00:05:00,310
Where?

79
00:05:06,080 --> 00:05:08,500
