90
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:32,110
Jin Xiao Rui.

91
00:05:32,640 --> 00:05:34,350
I got you something too.

92
00:05:34,520 --> 00:05:35,320
What did you prepare?

93
00:05:35,640 --> 00:05:36,590
Come on.

94
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:39,070
