after his dream girl left.

217
00:10:35,360 --> 00:10:36,160
He has missed her.

218
00:10:36,400 --> 00:10:38,430
It's the second minute
after his dream girl left.

219
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:40,030
He has missed her.

220
